      <title>new String(&quot;abc&quot;)创建了多少个对象？</title>
      <link>https://lovelxh95.github.io/2025/08/08/new-String-abc-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%AA%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%9F/</link>
